		   <br /><nobr><span id="notbold">Score</span>: Decent [2.90]</nobr><br /><br /><a href="/cgi-bin/pm.pl?action=addtolist&addname=RingMastah&type=Address" id="fs8"><img src="/shared/plus.gif" border="0" align="middle" height="9" width="9" alt="Add to address book"> Add to address book</a><br /><img src="/shared/transp.gif" width="135" border="0" height="1"></td><td valign="top" class="mform" width="100%"><p>I'm a LVL10 Enchanter and I'm already having a problem with too many spells to mem with only 8 spots to put them in. When i first enter group, I buff and Summon pet. Then i switch to combat mode i memorize : <br>1)Blind spell(will replace it with charm at LVL12)<br>2)Tash<br>3)Stun<br>4)Direct Damage<br>5)Weaken<br>6)DoT<br>7)Mesmerize<br>8)Root<br><br>Ok, now i know I'm gonna need to have a Slow, and a second stun, and a AOE Mez memorized along with other key spells when in a group, what should I replace?</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br />Venerable Ringmastah Waxmuseum<br>LVL65 Druid, 55AAs<br>Seventh Hammer<br>(RETIRED)<br>EQSUX!<br>Juggalotus(PVP)<br>LVL38 Undead Priest<br>WoWrox!</td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8"></td><td align="right" id="fs8" >6 Replies</td></tr></table>
